manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Why Choose Our Fitness Smartwatch? Our Stylish Newest Fitness Smart Watch, perfectly compatible with IOS Android, all functions support IOS 9.0 Android 5.0 and up smart phones. It is designed to help you learn more so you can achieve more. It goes beyond tracking steps and calories to offer actionable insights on everything from your running style. Sazooy smart watch is only to make your life smarter!

Highlight Features: •Full Touch Fitness Watch: View your health and exercise data on the 2.09 inch watch screen with a customizable dial. •7 Modes Activity Tracker: Support Running, Cycling, Basketball, Tennis, Volleyball, Football, Strength Training •Message Notifications: The watch can display text messages, calls and App notifications such as Facebook, WhatsApp, Twitter, LinkedIn, Instagram etc.(Note: Cannot Reply the Messages.) •Long Battery Life: Built-in Large capacity rechargeable battery, more than 7 days working time •Sport Record: Track your activities during your all day long •Pedometer Watch: Track your steps, calories burned, distance •Sleep Monitoring: Automatically monitor and analyze sleep quality •Music Control: Play and pause music through the watch When exercising, enjoy the passionate collision of sports and music.

All-day Activities Recorded When running, turn on the pedometer accurately record your steps,speed time and calories burned , walking mileage,activity times, Let you know more about your exercise status, help you stay active and maintain a healthy lifestyle. Remote Camera - Keep every beautiful moment Turn on remote control camera in app,you can take the picture from your wirst once watch paired with app. Brings more fun and convenience to you. Let it help u take beautiful photos and make good memories. Sedentary Reminder Life is movement, movement keeps the body healthy. Turn on the sedentary reminder function, which reminds you to get up and stretch your bones during a long time sitting still, helps you keep body in good state.

Message Notification After connecting to the phone, the fitness watch can receive most of the media message notifications and can reject the call on your wrist. It will let you never miss any important calls & message. Guided Breathing Sessions Follow the guide on this health tracker to take a deep breath to relax yourself from work stress, which makes you slow down your pace of breathing by having you apply deliberate effort in each breath. Smart Watches with Music Controller Wear your watch to exercise, connect to Bluetooth, easily control mobile phone music, and easily play your favorite playlist, allowing you to enjoy the dual relaxing experience of exercise + music.

Sleep monitoring Before going to bed every day, open the sleep mode, record your sleep time and sleep quality every night, let yourself know your sleep quality, let yourself develop a good routine, let life have a good state. Monitor sleep quality and record sleep status data. Just let it help u know more about yourself. Weather Forecast The smartwatch can show the current weather after watch is connected in the 'FitPro' app and the weather notification is turned on. Multi-functional Sazooy smart watch includes multiple other features, including Stopwatch, Timer, Alarm Clocks, Sedentary Reminders, Calendar, Calculator, Phone book, Two way Anti-lost, Muti-time zone, Muti-language, Games etc..

Warming reminder: Please charge it first to activate the watch the first time you receive it. We do not recommend that you wear this watch when diving, swimming in the sea, bathing or sauna. If the watch cannot be connected, it may be that the phone is connected to other devices. Please unbind other devices first. APP requirements: Android OS 5.0 / iOS 9.0 or above and Bluetooth 4. 2 or above smartphones.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good Smart Watch
reviews.reviewText: This is a nice inexpensive smart watch that has most of the features of the expensive ones. It does run a little slower but is to be expected with budget smart watch. It looks very similar to the Apple Watch. It works well with iPhone through their app. Would recommend for someone looking for a smart watch but not looking to spend the high price tag for an Apple Watch.
